            <h3>Generic method for Online Character Synthesis</h3>
            <h5>Guide:</h5><p>Dr.Srinivasa Chakravarthy.V, Computational Neuroscience Lab, IIT Madras (Aug'14 - present)</p>
            <h5>Abstract</h5>
            <p>
